description:
Associations and cooperatives that provide farm management
services or assistance in farming operations. Examples of such
services include financial assistance, management, or complete
maintenance of crops, soil preparation, planting and cultivating,
aerial dusting and spraying, disease and insect control, weed control,
and the harvesting of crops.
For merchants that provide farm product warehousing and storage,
use MCC 4225.
